notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-17T10:10:38.866Z",maintainer-agent,"Code evidence (2026-07-17 pass #95): context summary blocked counter at src/cli/commands/context.ts:1126-1132 increments only via isBlockedStatus(desc.status, statusRegistry) — status-only, no dependency-edge awareness; agenda ranking helpers at :675-682/:717 are likewise status-registry-driven. list-blocked is a status-filter list variant registered at src/cli/register-list-query.ts:656 (one of the 8 variants pm-pfqi consolidates). pm next's edge-aware definition (open_blocker_count from blocked_by deps, shipped for GH-489/pm-l0bu in PR#502) is the semantics to adopt. pm stats reports generic by-status buckets (honest labeling, NOT in scope). Fix belongs in a shared blocked-semantics helper consumed by next + context + list-blocked so pm-pfqi/pm-kcs4 consolidations inherit it."
body: ""
